HEADWORD: Flogger
<hw>Flog"ger</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
flogs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A kind of mallet for beating the bung stave of a
cask to start the bung.</def> <rj><au>Knight.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Flogging</ent>⟦br⟧
